@jreback: sorry that i'm creating unnecessary confusion. my understanding is that 0.24.1 is for regressions only. this PR is a bug fix and being concerned about potentially introducing a new regression, would prefer to see it go in 0.24.2.

The mention of 0.25 is because the fix could be seen as an unexpected change for a users perspective. This PR is not an api change.

